[32m│[0m #### **CRITICAL TOCTOU #1: Session Fixation Vulnerability**                  [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m **Vulnerability Description:**                                               [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - Session cookie is generated **BEFORE** user authentication                 [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - Same session cookie is reused **AFTER** successful authentication          [32m│[0m
