[32m│[0m USE:   Session cookie bMFJnx... grants authenticated access (post-auth)      [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m IMPACT: Full authentication bypass via session sharing                       [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m ```                                                                          [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
